NG0189:6694: phyag drug be con ral gri dgra s+t+wa g.yas //
NG0189:6695: g.yon pa sdigs mdzub mdung thung b+han dmar 'dzin //
NG0189:6696: be ta nag mo dgra s+t+wa dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6697: ral gcig sngon nag tri shul g.yang gzhi 'phyar //
NG0189:6698: sras mchog ya ma ra dza gshin rje gshed //
NG0189:6699: dbu gsum mthing nag g.yas dkar g.yon dmar zhal //
NG0189:6700: phyag drug 'khor lo ral gri lcags kyu g.yas /
NG0189:6701: kha t+wam dgra s+t+wa rgyu ma'i zhags pa g.yon //
NG0189:6702: g.yu yi ral gcig nag mo dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6703: lha mo dpal 'bar ral gri ne'u le 'dzin //
NG0189:6704: sras mchog myos byed 'bar ba gshin rje'i gshed //
NG0189:6705: dbu gsum g.yas sngo g.yon dmar dbus ser nag / phyag drug be con ral gri dgra s+t+wa g.yas //
NG0189:6706: g.yon pa b+han dmar 'khor lo lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0189:6707: gtum mo dug hrul ser nag b+han dmar stob /
NG0189:6708: khrag gi bdag mo spu gri tsit+ta 'dzin //
NG0189:6709: sras mchog gshin rje gshed po me ru tse //
NG0189:6710: dbu gsum g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar zhal //
NG0189:6711: phyag drug be con dbyug to kha t+wam g.yas //
NG0189:6712: b+han dmar 'khor lo rgyu ma'i zhags pa g.yon //
NG0189:6713: lha mo 'od zer dmar mo dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6714: gling bzhi gtsug 'byams snying dang b+han+d+ha stob //
NG0189:6715: sras mchog ral pa tshar dgu gshin rje'i gshed //
NG0189:6716: ljang nag g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus ljang zhal //
NG0189:6717: phyag drug be con gtun shing dgra s+t+wa g.yas //
NG0189:6718: b+han dmar rgyu zhags 'khor lo g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6719: bdud 'dul nag mo khram shing b+han+da g.yon //
NG0189:6720: srin mo mgo 'phyang dung khrag dgra sta 'phyar //
NG0189:6721: nag 'joms mthing nag rdo rje dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0189:6722: nag mo ral gcig yab 'khyud dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6723: phya sangs dkar po bum pa rdo rje gshol //
NG0189:6724: shel gyi gdong dgu yab 'khyud zangs gri thogs //
NG0189:6725: brag 'joms dkar ser brag dang 'khor lo 'dzin //
NG0189:6726: shel mig khro mo lcags kyu dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6727: glang mgo smug nag kha t+wam lcags kyu bsnams //
NG0189:6728: dkar skya mche gcig skar mda' dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6729: yab ti sngo nag ral gri lcags kyu 'dzin //
NG0189:6730: dred kyi a bsham khram shing b+han+d+ha thogs //
NG0189:6731: mig dmar smug nag ral gri dbyug pa g.yas /
NG0189:6732: khrag gi ral gcig g.yas g.yon dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6733: smig pa dud kha lcags sgrog phreng ba bsnams //
NG0189:6734: klu mo pus 'gro gtso la dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6735: tel pa sngo nag spu gri rak+ta 'dzin //
NG0189:6736: spyan gsum mche gtsigs b+han+d+ha rak+ta stob //
NG0189:6737: bdud 'joms smug nag tho ba b+han dmar bsnams //
NG0189:6738: smug nag ral cig yab la dung khrag stob //
NG0189:6739: chos rgyal dkar ser rdo rje khram nag 'dzin //
NG0189:6740: rdo rje ral gcig zhags pa dung dmar stob //
NG0189:6742: ba dmar po tses byang gtun shing 'dzin //
NG0189:6743: dmar mo mgo dgu tri shul b+han dmar stob //
NG0189:6744: thod dbyug mthing nag zhing dbyug sho rde'u bsnams //
NG0189:6745: nag mo phag mgo zhags pa thod khrag stob /
NG0189:6746: dung gi rgod mgo rdo rje lcags kyu bsnams *//
NG0189:6747: nag mo stag mgo rin chen zhags pa 'dzin //
NG0189:6748: kang ka dmar po pad+ma lcags sgrog 'dzin //
NG0189:6749: ljang nag spyang mgo rgya gram dril bu 'dzin //
NG0189:6750: bde bar gshegs pa sku mchog 'dus pa'i gtso //
NG0189:6751: rang rig phyag rgya'i mchod pa bzhes su gsol //
NG0189:6752: nub phyogs dkyil 'khor lha rnams 'dus pa'i gtso //
NG0189:6753: bcom ldan dpal chen rta mgrin rgyal po'i sku //
NG0189:6754: dmar nag dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0189:6755: dbu gsum g.yas dkar g.yon sngo dbus dmar zhal //
NG0189:6756: phyag drug rdo rje kha t+wam sbrul zhags g.yas //
NG0189:6757: dril bu b+han dmar lcags sgrog g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6758: e ka dza ti kha t+wam dung khrag stob //
NG0189:6759: sprul pa phra men las kyi rgyal po gnyis //
NG0189:6760: zhal gcig phyag gnyis sku mdog dmar nag 'bar //
NG0189:6761: phyag gnyis so sor rdo rje thod phrag dang *//
NG0189:6762: rdo rje ri rab phur pa 'dzin zhing 'dril //
NG0189:6763: dpal chen sprul pa'i zil gnon khro bo brgyad //
NG0189:6764: dmar nag dbu+u gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi bgrad //
NG0189:6765: dbu gtsug rta mgo rta skad thengs gsum 'byin //
NG0189:6766: zhi ba'i lha rnams zil gnon rta mgrin ni //
NG0189:6767: phyag drug 'khor lo rdo rje rin chen g.yas //
NG0189:6768: pad+ma ral gri dril bu g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6769: brkyang bskum zhabs kyis zhi ba rigs lnga gnon //
NG0189:6770: mi pham khro mo sku la dgyes par 'khril //
NG0189:6771: las kyi khro bo zil gnon khro bcu gnon //
NG0189:6772: phyag drug pad+ma dbyug tho spu gri g.yas /
NG0189:6773: kha t+wam dgra s+t+wa rgya gram g.yon na bsnams /
NG0189:6774: khro gnyer dmar mo sku la dgyes par 'khril //

NG0189:6776: phyag drug sdigs mdzub lcags kyu 'phrul zhags g.yas //
NG0189:6777: lcags sgrog rnga chung kha t+wam g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6778: ro langs dmar mo sku+u la dgyes par 'khril /

NG0189:6780: phyag drug rdo rje sa dang me khyung g.yas //
NG0189:6781: nam mkha' chu rlung bya khyung g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6782: spyan gcig dmar mo sku+u la dgyes par 'khril //
NG0189:6783: pho rgyud zil gnon dregs pa'i lha brgyad gnon //
NG0189:6784: phyag drug rdo rje thod khrag rgyu zhags g.yas //
NG0189:6785: dung khrag thod rlon zhing dbyug g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6786: rdo rje las byed dmar mo sku+u la 'khril //
NG0189:6787: mi rgyud zil gnon ma bdun sring bzhi gnon //
NG0189:6788: phyag drug rdo rje ral gri mda' ni g.yas // zhags pa sdigs mdzub gzhu ni g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6789: gshin rje las byed dmar mo sku+u la 'khril //
NG0189:6790: klu rnams zil gnon gdug pa'i sbrul brgyad gnon //
NG0189:6791: phyag drug sbrul dkar ser dmar g.yas na bsnams //
NG0189:6792: sbrul khra sbrul ljang nag po g.yon na bsnams //
NG0189:6793: klu mo las byed dmar mo sku la @#//
NG0189:6795: gza' rnams zil gnon nyi zla gza' brgyad gnon //
NG0189:6796: phyag drug rdo rje zhags pa ral gri g.yas //
NG0189:6797: dung khrag seng sdeng dbyug pa khyung nag g.yon //
NG0189:6798: gnod sbyin las byed dmar mo sku la 'khril //

NG0189:6800: sgo bzhi'i pho nya dkar ser dmar ljang mdog / lcags kyu zhags pa lcags sgrog dril bu 'dzin //

NG0189:6802: rang rig phyag rgya'i mchod pa zhes su gsol //
NG0189:6803: byang phyogs dkyil 'khor lha rnams 'dus pa'i gtso //
NG0189:6804: bcom ldan dpal chen rdo rje gzhon nu'i sku //
NG0189:6805: dbu gsum phyag drug zhabs bzhi sku mdog mthing *//
NG0189:6806: dbu gsum g.yas dkar g.yon dmar dbus mthing zhal /

NG0189:6810: 'khor lo rgyas 'debs kha t+wam thod khrag stob //

NG0189:6817: phyag drug dang po be con dgra s+t+wa bsnams //
NG0189:6818: bar ma gnyis ni rin chen ral gri bsnams //

NG0189:6826: bar ma gnyis na lcags kyur ral gri 'dzin //

NG0189:6857: bar ma'i phyag gnyis rdo rje sbrul zhags bsnams //
NG0189:6858: rdo rje skul byed gri gug dung khrag stob //
NG0189:6859: yab yum sprul pa dam tsha dom dang sre mo'i
NG0189:6860: mgo / stobs chen dud kha mthing nag ljang gu'i
NG0189:6861: zhal // bar ma gnyis na tho ba zhags pa bsnams //

NG0189:6868: rdo rje ri rab phur pa 'dril zhing 'debs //

NG0189:6878: phyag drug rdo rje sbrul khyung sbrul zhags g.yas //
NG0189:6879: b+han+d+ha zhing lpags ga'u g.yon na bsnams //

NG0189:6881: dbu gcig zhal lnga phyag drug phyag mtshan ni //

NG0189:6883: dril bu b+han+d+ha g.yang gzhi g.yon na bsnams //

NG0189:6889: bar ma gnyis na me dbal dbyug tho bsnams //
NG0189:6890: tha ma'i phyag gis stag mo zhing phran
